The paper discusses a data-driven framework for policy learning in connected and autonomous vehicles, which involves machine learning and control algorithms. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV). Among these, cs.AI and cs.RO are the most likely categories, as they directly relate to the development of autonomous vehicles and their decision-making capabilities. The other categories are also relevant, as they involve machine learning and control algorithms, which are used in the proposed framework.
